metadata.description: Welcome to the 40 ETH Rekt Raffle Giveaway! The largest, fairest & highest probability of winning blockchain raffle to date! There will be 3 lucky winners. 1st place wins 32 ETH, 2nd place wins 5 ETH, & 3rd place wins 3 ETH. Each ticket holds a 3 out of 3333 chance of being 1 of 3 lucky winners of ETH. As well as some other surprises for all ticket holders
